---
title: Parmesan-Crusted Baked Tilapia with Buttered Rice and Lemony Mayo
description: These beautiful tilapia fillets are topped with Parmesan and a generous heap of herbed panko that bakes to crunchy, buttery perfection! If that wasn't enough, a touch of lemon mayo takes this fish dinner to the next level. Basmati rice and green beans are simple but satisfying sides.
